    "templateOptions": {
      "expressionLock": "formState.memoria.tipo === 'RATIFICACION'",
      "label": "4.4 Information and consent"
    },
    "fieldGroup": [
      {
        "template": "<p>Is the consent of the participant/source and/or their legal representative requested?</p>"
      },
      {
        "wrappers": [
          "info-div"
        ],
        "template": "<p>So that the participation of a person as a study subject in research can be truly considered <strong>free and voluntary</strong> should first receive <strong>suitable</strong> information that can be given orally, written and/or audiovisual.</p><p><strong>The information and subsequent consent process should be documented on a sheet</strong> that collects the signatures and the minimum mandatory information but may be accompanied by other helpful information materials such as brochures, booklets, slides, videos, multimedia, etc.) aimed at informing the participating subject and therefore directed and appropriate in language and form to her characteristics.</p><p>The document that contains the consent itself does not have legal validity if it is not proven that the necessary information has been provided to the participant.</p><p>To learn more about the minimum mandatory information, consult:</p><ul><li>Articles <a href='http://www.boe.es/buscar/act.php?id=BOE-A-2007-12945&p=20110602&tn=1#a15' target='_blank'>fifteen</a>, <a href='http://www.boe.es/buscar/act.php?id=BOE-A-2007-12945&p=20110602&tn=1#a47' target='_blank'>47</a>, <a href='http://www.boe.es/buscar/act.php?id=BOE-A-2007-12945&p=20110602&tn=1#a59' target='_blank'>59 and 60</a> of LIB 14/2007.</li></ul>"
      },
      {
        "key": "informacionConsentimientoRadio",
        "type": "radio",
        "templateOptions": {
          "required": true,
          "label": "Choose an option:",
          "options": [
            {
              "value": "no",
              "label": "No"
            },
            {
              "value": "si",
              "label": "Yes"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "fieldGroup": [
          {
            "template": "Please indicate the reason why it is not requested"
          },
          {
            "key": "informacionConsentimientoMotivoRadio",
            "type": "radio",
            "templateOptions": {
              "required": true,
              "label": "Choose an option",
              "options": [
                {
                  "value": "anonimizados",
                  "label": "Samples/anonymised data"
                },
                {
                  "value": "otros",
                  "label": "Other"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        ],
        "hideExpression": "!model.informacionConsentimientoRadio || model.informacionConsentimientoRadio === 'si'"
      },
      {
        "template": "<p>Please specify or justify</p>",
        "hideExpression": "!((model.informacionConsentimientoRadio && model.informacionConsentimientoRadio === 'no') && (model.informacionConsentimientoMotivoRadio && model.informacionConsentimientoMotivoRadio === 'otros'))"
      },
      {
        "key": "informacionConsentimientoMotivoTexto",
        "type": "i18n-textarea",
        "hideExpression": "!((model.informacionConsentimientoRadio && model.informacionConsentimientoRadio === 'no') && (model.informacionConsentimientoMotivoRadio && model.informacionConsentimientoMotivoRadio === 'otros'))",
        "templateOptions": {
          "label": "Please specify or justify",
          "placeholder": "Please specify or justify",
          "required": true,
          "autosize": true,
          "autosizeMinRows": "1",
          "autosizeMaxRows": "10"
        }
      },
      {
        "wrappers": [
          "info-div"
        ],
        "template": "<p>Note: add the consent form as well as all the auxiliary information material that has been prepared in section '5.1 Consent document'.</p>"
      }
    ]
  }
]